{"tid":2245477,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［又係鄭紀航條撚屌］17歲男生僅藏索帶士巴拿打火機 官推論至拆欄縱火裁定罪成還柙候判","createTime":"2020-10-16T09:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T09:39:03.000Z","uid":239336,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03918ef40579d39152ce1bd2c9ef06f1fe1d91cb","tid":2245477,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:03:47.000Z","msg":"網民去年11月11日連日發動「大三罷」，西灣河一帶有堵路事件，其間一名17歲學生在西灣河街頭遭防暴警搜出一包未開封的索帶、士巴拿及打火機等物品，因而被控。男生不認罪，早前受審。裁判官鄭紀航今裁定管有適合作非法用途工具及管有物品意圖摧毀及損毀財產兩罪成立。鄭官全盤接納三名警員的證供，並形容被告砌詞狡辯，謊話連篇，更推論涉案物品是被告取自家中帶往現場，欲作拆欄杆、綁欄杆和縱火之用。被告還柙至本月29日，其間索取勞教中心及教導所報告。<br />\n<br />\n鄭官裁決時指，控方三位警方證人誠實可靠，全盤接納他們的口供，反指被告既不可信，亦不可靠。鄭官一口氣指斥被告作供「前言不對後語、自圓其說、堆砌情節、砌詞狡辯、謊話連篇」，並指被告任職路政署工程督察的父親作供時亦見迴避，模棱兩可。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201015/TUREYOSI5VC5HBRQAXQNP2QLBI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201015%2FTUREYOSI5VC5HBRQAXQNP2QLBI%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVUw7Fv2waV%2FkF2w15sEbuDLw%3D&h=a7a830a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201015%2FTUREYOSI5VC5HBRQAXQNP2QLBI%2F&h=eb538e3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201015/TUREYOSI5VC5HBRQAXQNP2QLBI/</a>"},{"pid":"c9b1bbad9ce302525f619e902a9052b0c6476529","tid":2245477,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9fd58041797f3ff48e1b78b4fe297b4bb7ab14","tid":2245477,"uid":46309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:09:12.000Z","msg":"又係呢條仆街官"},{"pid":"3ae721103fc2c2d1470b418ef2a9ea3e986b8e94","tid":2245477,"uid":42760,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"坐監師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c40f62ff2adf72b9fced7